OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775571065
OL,3,CLifeguard warning after teenagers
OL,4,Csaved from powerful rip current
OL,6,FVolunteer lifeguards are warning of
OL,7,Fdangerous swells on Cornish beaches
OL,8,Fafter rescuing a group of teenagers
OL,9,Ffrom a rip current on Bank Holiday
OL,10,FMonday (Monday 6 April).
OL,12,FGyllyngvase Surf Life Saving Club were
OL,13,Fpatrolling Gyllyngvase Beach in
OL,14,FFalmouth between 11am and 1pm, on
OL,15,Ftheir first day of the season, when
OL,16,Fthe group was swept out to sea.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
