FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775571065
OL,3,CLifeguard warning after teenagers
OL,4,Csaved from powerful rip current
OL,6,FVolunteer lifeguards and off-duty RNLI
OL,7,FLifeguard Matthew Stone brought the
OL,8,Fgroup back to safety.
OL,10,FMatthew said: "Despite its typically
OL,11,Fcalm appearance, Gyllyngvase can
OL,12,Fbecome extremely dangerous during
OL,13,Fstrong easterly and southerly winds,
OL,14,Fas can many beaches along the south
OL,15,Fcoast.
OL,17,F"Where there are waves, there are rip
OL,18,Fcurrents. If you are unsure of the
OL,19,Fconditions, do not enter the water.
OL,26,@rD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
