PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775571065
OL,3,CLifeguard warning after teenagers
OL,4,Csaved from powerful rip current
OL,6,F"There is a particularly strong rip
OL,7,Fcurrent on the right-hand side of the
OL,8,Fbeach, near the sauna, during easterly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,11,F"We strongly advise beach users to
OL,12,Favoid entering the water in this area
OL,13,Funder those conditions."
OL,15,F"If you see someone in difficulty,
OL,16,Fcall 999 and ask for the Coastguard."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@XO]wD@AOUxD@eO]
